erDiagram
  %% Southville 8B NHS Edge - Public schema ERD
  %% Following Gliffy ERD principles: https://www.gliffy.com/blog/how-to-draw-an-entity-relationship-diagram
  %%
  %% Components:
  %% - Entities: Tables represented as rectangles with attributes listed inside
  %% - Attributes: Properties of entities (columns with data types)
  %% - Relationships: Actions/verbs describing how entities interact (e.g., "Has", "Creates", "Belongs to")
  %% - Cardinality: Numerical relationships between entities
  %%
  %% Notation:
  %% - PK marks primary keys
  %% - Data types taken from Postgres (snake_case preserved)
  %% - Relationships use verb-based labels (following Gliffy principles)
  %% - Cardinality: ||--o{ = one-to-many, ||--|| = one-to-one, }o--o{ = many-to-many

